Comment: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:22.52,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:28.15,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.11,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.99,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.18,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:46.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:51.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:58.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:04.77,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:13.96,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:19.16,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:30.78,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Never say Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a scorching sun, nor a violent wind, \Nnor a hot heart that burns inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are unable to stop the autumn \Nfrom coming into my damned life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only later when I came to the understanding \Nthat this summer was nothing special in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Tokyo Cup is... \NJust a week away now, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making any progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you had a word from Todo since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have no idea when is he coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:15.04,Default,ep title,0,0,100,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&H5C9699&\t(0,700,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H6999B0&)\c&HFBFAF9&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx182\fscy148}Episode 4\N\N\N\N\NTodo, I want to see you.....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how, but something made him sure \Nin her coming to see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, even when the flight was minutes away, \Nwas unwilling to leave his café seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was waiting for her. \NHe knew for sure that Oka would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is... While Todo was at the shrine \Nwith coach Katsura, they started to miss each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, how long do you know \Nabout what is between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's and Todo's feelings... Wouldn't surprise me \Neven if I didn't know about them for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,From her very first appearance at Nishi High, \NOka was already kinda fond of Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo and Oka have always been warm to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka is only nineteen, \Nand Todo is already twenty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, they are similar. They are both not flighty at all \Nand think that first you like the person, then you love 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, \Nthey were destined to come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... How come that both for Todo and for Oka, \Nthe prime moments of their lives are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's left... Is to watch from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have... \NBeen in love with Oka yourself, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So ardently that I felt my heart burning. \NSo ardently that I didn't dare to say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left for us now \Nis to watch silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So... He didn't try to contact you either?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no surprise, if you ask me. He promised to contact us \Nonce a week, so we shouldn't expect him to do it more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he might be too busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,New York will soon be hosting the US championship, \Nand he has to prepare for the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he can't find time for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, though... If I remember well, \Nthese qualifiers have ended two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1800)}Then, no doubt, he's successfully passed the first tour \Nand is now preparing for the real matches with might and main.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly doesn't seem to know... \NAbout these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's better! Then, let's try now \Nhitting the line by ballistic trajectory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim to drive the ball more accurately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't lose your balance while running!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten days have passed since you left. \NHow have you been doing there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was New York a welcoming place? \NAnd, of course... Are you doing fine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx100}You know... Each day I'm more and more eager to hear from you, \Nmy heart trembles every time the phone rings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I'm sure that you'd rather write me a letter \Nbecause that'll be so much like you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I look forward to it. Because this way, \NI can find out what Todo's New York address is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as soon as that happens, \NI will write you letters every single day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tokyo Cup is approaching relentlessly, \Nand my practices are getting harder too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I will always have time \Nto write you a letter every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe, my writings are not gonna be \Nsomething informative or constructive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I will still send them, \Ncause that's the only thing that makes my heart flutter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you given us a single word so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka... New York has... \NTurned out to be a very rainy place. Oka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,International call, please.\NTo New York, 211...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day \NI tried to reach New York by the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Todo already gave you \Nhis current phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. My university has \Nits established correspondent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He also knows Todo well, \Nso I asked him if he is in any way aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior, is that you? Chiba talks. \NI'm happy to hear from you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard about that one match \Nhappened two days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, some strange letter came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An airmail one. \NDo you know someone in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi? I'll leave it on the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing fine? \NNew York has turned out to be a very rainy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got myself a small apartment \Nnear Central Park on one of the avenues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The building is quite old, \Nbut the area is quiet and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll tell you about everything that happened \Nand why I didn't write before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, for coming to the airport to see me off, \Nthank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we didn't have enough time to sit there \Nand talk without a hurry... But I'm still happy that you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In this huge airport lobby, \Nyou looked so confused, desperately looking for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This moment has become the most precious gem for me \Nthat I will hardly ever forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I wasn't even sure \NI should write that very letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, by the moment you are reading this, \Nmy first match in America is already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I positively intend to win it \Nso that I could move on to my next goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And to you... With the Tokyo Cup, I wish best of luck too. \NI believe the next letter would follow quite soon. Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Last ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight! Last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not playing the way you usually do. \NYou emit some kind of delight today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you'll never cease to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Among all the skillful athletes that I've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the first one able to clear your mind perfectly \Nand focus on how you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell the truth! \NNothing is different in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not happier than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Munakata tried to kill that trait of yours... But he failed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Didn't you just say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Munakata was... Munakata Jin was probably \Nthe most of all afraid of this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100}Athletes whose way of playing depends on the state of their mind \Ncan play like true geniuses while they're happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but when they feel bad, \Nthey play like a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how beautiful whatever is on your mind now... \NYou should put it aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki and Chiba are here today. \NI came to ask if you would like to dine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! With great pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba, Ozaki, \Nthat Chinese treat was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. Ozaki's idea. At such a moment, \Nhe wanted to encourage you two in any way he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I had to miss the Tokyo Cup myself, I decided to support \Nthe ones who will defend Nishi High's honor on behalf of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But ain't Todo in New York \Ndefending it in the best way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was Todo who made us come together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My New York acquaintance answered me \Nabout how he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo has finished his first match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,6-1, 6-2, 6-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! I had no doubt Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Todo has... Lost this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was raining on the court that day, \Nand only about fifty spectators came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent was the rising pro \Nwith a three hundredth spot in the rankings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Todo seemed to control \Nneither his legs nor his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was only the qualifiers for qualifiers. \NBut the Japan championship winner Todo couldn't pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One high wall rose between him and the world level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to believe it... \NBut that's just a plain fact that we have to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo has lost... Could someone imagine such a thing? \NI had no idea that was even possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is still worthy. His spirit is strong. \NHe is used to challenging himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, even one or two defeats \Nwon't make him completely upset and disheartened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That last one point...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it's scored, victory is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And my fighting spirit will have no rest, \Nchasing the ball further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However... \NThe moment the match is declared finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have to humbly leave the court.\N And even if it'll make me spill a tear, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... What you declared a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100}You said Todo who has been playing tennis since elementary school...\NHas already passed the peak of his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And that by becoming a pro now he will only doom himself \Nto not having a single chance to get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the top is exactly the destination of the Todo's path...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From my point of view, \Nthat's what you wanted to convey to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to get me wrong, Hiromi. \NIn fact, I just... I just expressed my own point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because I was sure \Nthat Todo is feeling it the same way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And look by yourself: a wall between him and the real pros' \Nworld turned out to be too high to climb over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he is carrying way more courage than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NHe'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter whether he wins or loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose is him getting an answer \Nfor what's bothering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go visit him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. If his own confidence abandons him, \Nhe'll have a friendly shoulder to lean on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget that most of all, he would be offended now \Nby someone's sympathy and pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your today's opponent is younger than you. \NShe's a second-year, high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At the junior tournament, she performed well enough.\NThe All-Japan school championship was won by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Oka Hiromi\N-vs-\NSekiguchi Namiko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, today it is more than ever important \Nto put your feelings aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you unbound your mind, \Nyour soul's distress will wreak havoc in your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coach... I'm sorry. No matter how hard I tried to expel \Nthese thoughts from my heart... They just refuse to go away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This morning... \NI received the second letter from Todo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was from America saying that Todo has \Nfinished his second game too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, that letter didn't contain a single word \Nregarding the outcome of his game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is so devastating... Even though I'm trying \Nas hard, as usual, I can't stop worrying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything he wrote was \Nhow much he is concerned about me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, are you doing fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, by the time you receive this letter, \Nyour first Tokyo Cup game will be already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can easily imagine you running around the court again, \Ntirelessly as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember how strong your serve was, \Nyour bunny-like bouncy smash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course... Those incredible aces of yours \Nthat make you smile so sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Game! One game to three!\NSekiguchi lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Hiromi \NSekiguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to perform a brilliant victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I could be liberated from worries torturing me. \NTherefore, Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To New York, the autumn came unexpectedly quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In a blink of an eye, Central Park lost all of its greenery, \Nand the wind became so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After two more weeks, I suppose, the falling leaves will start \Ndancing their way to the ground. But for now, see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That one last point... \NUntil it is scored, I still can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And until that happens, my spirit won't rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,making me run after the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However... The moment the match is considered over,\NI will have to humbly leave the court, regardless of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, while standing on the court after the match, \Nunconsciously, a few small but bitter tears... I shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven games to five. Two games to six.\NLove game to six. Two sets to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Hiromi\NSekiguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Match won by... Sekiguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Hiromi? \NIt was supposed to be an easy game...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka... I was sincerely hoping that at this championship, \NI'll have a chance to compete with you fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something heavy... \NLaid on me today, not allowing me to move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? \NWell, don't worry about it. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, I... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a chance to enter the second tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This championship uses \Nthe double-elimination rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Six days after the first defeat, \Nthe loser is allowed to play a repêchage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure that in the repêchage match \Nyou won't look as pitiful as today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then I'll listen to your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't forget that most of all, \Nhe would be offended now by someone's sympathy and pity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The autumn in New York has started \Nunexpectedly quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The greenery of Central Park \Nis swiftly losing its color...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the wind has suddenly become so cold. \NJust two more weeks, and I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The falling leaves... \NWill begin to dance their way to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is wrong... \NNo one deserves to be left without sympathy and pity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let this happen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wrong, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I so much... Want to see Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Hiromi was admitted to the repechage match, \Nshe told coach Katsura she won't play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In response, coach Katsura blurted on hiromi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should make a decision \Nof what matters to you the most right now!'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go to New York to see Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "No turning back now."